metadata.name: The Guru Llama
metadata.description:
The Guru Llama. Generative artwork inspired by and painted in collaboration with Da Vinci.

Welcome to the coolest digital art collection around - the Llamas in Shades collection! These AI-supported, beautiful and unique pieces of art have been inspired by and painted in cooperation with some of the world's most famous artists, and they are simply too cool to ignore.

Each piece features a unique Llama wearing a pair of sunglasses, and the effect is simply awesome. From the colorful paintings inspired by Monet to the distinctive pieces inspired by Da Vinci, these fancy Llamas will definitely stand out in your digital art collection. 

Become part of an exclusive community that understands the allure of a Llama in Shades.
